Package com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services

package com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services
The services subpackage under responsebodies contains service implementations related to processing and post-processing responses in the Pandora Freshwaters Biogeochemistry application controllers. These services implement the interfaces defined in the corresponding services subpackage. * The package includes the following service interfaces:
  • CellCalculationResponseService:

    Interface for services handling cell calculation responses.

  • SpeciesResponseService:

    Interface for services handling species response data.

The main service implementations in this package include:

  • CellCalculationReponseServiceImpl:

    Implementation of the CellCalculationResponseService for processing and post-processing cell calculation responses.

  • SpeciesResponseServiceImpl:

    Implementation of the SpeciesResponseService for processing and post-processing species response data.

These service implementations provide concrete logic for handling and transforming response data within the PANDORA API.
